header: Pharaoh Too Will Descend to the Grave

verse: In the twelfth year, in the twelfth month, on the first day of the month, the word of the Lord came to me.
Son of man, raise a lament over Pharaoh, the king of Egypt, and say this to him.
In the twelfth year, on the fifteenth day of the month, the word of the Lord came to me.
